  "title": "Simply Airdrops",
  "description": "Simply Airdrops is a lightweight and easy-to-use mod that does exactly what the name suggests — it adds dynamic airdrop events to your world.",
  "body": "<iframe width=\"560\" height=\"315\" src=\"https://www.youtube-nocookie.com/embed/JI46iCIS5QA\" title=\"YouTube video player\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share\" allowfullscreen></iframe>\n<p align=\"center\">\n  <img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/RKStudios-hub/pixelart-assets/main/new.png\">\n</p>\n\n<p align=\"center\">\n  <img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/RKStudios-hub/pixelart-assets/main/line.png\" width=\"400\">\n</p> \n\n<p align=\"center\">\n  <b>Lightweight • Customisable • Event-Based Airdrops</b>\n</p>\n\n<p align=\"center\">\n  <img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/RKStudios-hub/pixelart-assets/main/line.png\" width=\"400\">\n</p>\n\n\n\n<p align=\"center\">\n  <b>✨ Features</b><br>\n  Includes timed airdrop events with configurable intervals, a radio controller for manually triggering drops, custom loot tables and crate types, a JSON-driven configuration system, and seamless compatibility with other mods.\n</p>\n\n<br>\n\n\n\n<p align=\"center\">\n  <img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/RKStudios-hub/pixelart-assets/main/2026-04-06_19.45.23.png\">\n  <img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/RKStudios-hub/pixelart-assets/main/2026-04-06_20.25.05.png\">\n</p>\n\n<p align=\"center\">\n  <img width=\"400\" alt=\"divider\" src=\"https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/a796531e-5f22-4a58-9476-d99b5015a1b4\" />\n</p>\n\n<!-- SOCIALS -->\n<p align=\"center\">\n  <a href=\"https://discord.gg/VrcVft4GEf\"><img src=\"https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/3d4e037e-2e65-4f5d-ab71-8a46ba8a60a7\" width=\"60\" height=\"60\" alt=\"Discord\"/></a>\n  &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\n  <a href=\"#\"><img src=\"https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/2d3adbcc-01ce-4c01-82ef-82c628cbc20f\" width=\"60\" height=\"60\" alt=\"Twitter\"/></a>\n  &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\n  <a href=\"#\"><img src=\"https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/cf2a5174-83ae-4f22-9015-3ec21263d550\" width=\"60\" height=\"60\" alt=\"Like\"/></a>\n  &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\n  <a href=\"#\"><img src=\"https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/8d846e2a-e4b4-4502-ab7f-3ab2590e1e32\" width=\"60\" height=\"60\" alt=\"YouTube\"/></a>\n  &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\n  <a href=\"#\"><img src=\"https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/2d416633-6809-4f5f-85cd-bb17d4ddf0f0\" width=\"60\" height=\"60\" alt=\"Donate\"/></a>\n</p>\n\n<p align=\"center\">\n  <img width=\"400\" alt=\"divider\" src=\"https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/a796531e-5f22-4a58-9476-d99b5015a1b4\" />\n</p>\n\n<br>\n\n<p align=\"center\">\n  <b>⚙️ Compatibility</b><br>\n  Built for Forge and supports Minecraft 1.20.1.\n</p>\n\n<br>\n\n<div align=\"center\">\n  <strong>📦 Requirements</strong><br>\n  Requires GeckoLib for animated block models.<br><br>\n  <strong>Note:</strong> From version v1.0.5 onwards, the mod requires Cloth Config.\n</div>\n<br>\n\n<div align=\"center\">\n  <img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/RKStudios-hub/pixelart-assets@main/geckolib.png\" width=\"300\">\n</div>\n\n\n\n<p align=\"center\">\n  <img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/RKStudios-hub/pixelart-assets/main/line.png\" width=\"400\">\n</p> \n\n<p align=\"center\">\n  <b>🛠️ Made by</b><br>\n  RK Studios\n</p>\n\n<br>\n\n<p align=\"center\">\n  <b>💬 Notes</b><br>\n  🚧 Still being improved<br>\n  ✨ More features coming soon\n</p>\n\n<br>\n\n<p align=\"center\">\n  <b>📢 Feedback</b><br>\n  Found a bug or have an idea?<br>\n  → Open an issue on GitHub\n</p>\n\n<p align=\"center\">\n  <img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/RKStudios-hub/pixelart-assets/main/line.png\" width=\"400\">\n</p> \n\n<p align=\"center\">\n  <img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/RKStudios-hub/pixelart-assets/main/thankyou.png\" width=\"400\">\n</p>\n",
